{"tid":1049304,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"關仁隱事：「攞錯嘢」偕夫名店尋仇 - 關仁","createTime":"2019-03-06T07:23:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T10:31:20.000Z","uid":11512,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6f1f5818094a860c67f80dd6eda1598e5633fd24","tid":1049304,"uid":11512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T07:23:18.000Z","msg":"歌星「攞錯嘢」喺樂壇最令人津津樂道嘅係佢亂咁攞人嘢嘅事件，不過佢好彩釣到隻金龜出錢出力幫佢開演唱會。其實之前攞錯嘢去到金鐘某名店買嘢嗰陣，要人落閘等佢慢慢shopping俾人拒絕嘅事已經係人都知，點知第二日佢帶埋老公去「尋仇」，仲指明搵番早一日拒絕佢嘅職員招呼，又話display啲衫太舊，要人開新衫畀佢試，個職員明知佢玩嘢都惟有照做，當開到第七件新衫時，個職員好為難咁話唔可以再拆新衫，佢老公卒之等到位入，大叫：「家係咪我哋買唔起，冇錢買。」之後就連寄兩封信去投訴，卒之搞到人哋份工都冇埋。<br />\n撰文：關仁"},{"pid":"c24379b516bd0075040a79004d77e32099cc91bb","tid":1049304,"uid":52339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T07:25:24.000Z","msg":"家姐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8268ab4e004eceffd24eba5e634d648566aa2f17","tid":1049304,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T07:28:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b867ecb6b6080633e622187ad1126cc795d7e28c","tid":1049304,"uid":36894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T09:09:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f7d3f6f7c8813be694e7f27efb6abebee0a529","tid":1049304,"uid":17853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c24379b516bd0075040a79004d77e32099cc91bb","tid":1049304,"uid":52339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T07:25:24.000Z","msg":"家姐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T09:30:23.000Z","msg":"應該係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />攞錯獎"},{"pid":"de047a97c68caf26f3156f8593e40382bc7c2cd7","tid":1049304,"uid":154106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T09:40:12.000Z","msg":"又係佢&hellip;<br />\n唔厭嫁？"}